snippet.title: PLAYING GOD - Release Trailer
snippet.description:
God is missing. Hell is full. Someone has taken over, and now souls must earn their place to stay in hell. Speedrun your way across the nine circles of hell through 90 levels in this ultra fast-paced precision platformer, rebelling against the mysterious entity playing god.

Check it out now on Steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/3165320/Playing_God/
